<view class="page recharge-page" style="{{appearanceStyle}}">
  <view class="balance-card"><text>账户余额</text><text class="balance">¥0.00</text><text>开发期暂未绑定正式会员账户</text></view>
  <view class="section-title"><text>充值金额</text><text>{{message}}</text></view>
  <view class="rule-grid" wx:if="{{rules.length}}">
    <view class="rule {{selectedRuleId === item.id ? 'selected' : ''}}" wx:for="{{rules}}" wx:key="id" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="chooseRule"><text>¥{{item.rechargeText}}</text><text wx:if="{{item.giftCents}}">赠 ¥{{item.giftText}}</text><text wx:else>{{item.name}}</text></view>
  </view>
  <view class="unavailable" wx:elif="{{!loading}}"><text>储值功能暂未开放</text><text>这里已经预留储值规则展示。真实充值会在支付通道、余额账本、退款和对账全部验收后启用。</text></view>
  <view class="empty" wx:else>正在加载充值规则…</view>
  <view class="safety"><text>资金安全说明</text><text>当前页面不会发起支付，也不会生成余额；避免出现“付款成功但余额未到账”的资金风险。</text></view>
  <button class="primary recharge-button" disabled="{{!available}}" bindtap="recharge">{{available ? '立即充值' : '暂未开放'}}</button>
</view>
